function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

 //event listener function to call markhelpful function on each load of new ratings

function callHelpfulEvent(){
            document.querySelectorAll('.FM_hlp_rvw').forEach(item => {
                
                    item.addEventListener('click', event => {
                        
                        var im_iss = getCartCookie("im_iss");
                        if(im_iss == ""){
                           signIn('','','','B');
                            return;
                        }
                         var is_imesh = readCookie("ImeshVisitor");
                         var rat_glid='';
                         if(is_imesh != ""){
                           rat_glid=getparamVal(is_imesh, "glid");
                         }
                        var ip_cookie = getCartCookie("iploc");
                        var ip=''; var country='';
                        if(ip_cookie!= ""){
                            ip=getparamVal(ip_cookie, "gip");
                            country=getparamVal(ip_cookie, "gcnnm");
                        }
                        
                        markHelpful(rat_glid,item.id,1,source_id,ip,country); //calling markhelpful function for testimonial
                    });
                });
            }
            //for calling the helful functionality on first page load
            $(document).ready(function(){
    callHelpfulEvent();
});
function getRatingAjax(){
        $.ajax({
            type: "POST",
            url: '/prod-fcp/files/review_rating.php',
            dataType: 'json',
            data : {input_supplier_id:decryptedglid, sort_type:sort_type,pagelinktype:pagelinktype, is_presnt_tstmonial:is_presnt_tstmonial, testimonialPageLink:testimonialPageLink,limit:limit},
            success: function(response)
            {
                if(response != ''){
                    if(response.resultTop !="undefined" && response.resultTop !=""){
                        $("#review_data").html(response.resultTop);
                        if(response.resultComments !="undefined" && response.resultComments !="" && (pagelinktype == 'testimonial' || pagelinktype == 'demotestimonial'))
                            $("#commentHTML").html(response.resultComments);
                        
                }
                }
            },
            beforeSend: function(){
                $('.loader').show();
            },
            complete: function(){
                $('.loader').hide();
                callHelpfulEvent();
            },
            error: function(error) {
                console.log(error.responseText);
            }
        });
    }

    $('.FM_sortng').change(function(){
       limit = 20;
        sort_type = $('#sortValue').val();
        if(limit<$total_rating)
            {$("#rat_more").show();}
        else{
            $("#rat_more").hide();}
        if(limit==20)
        getRatingAjax();
        else
        getPaginatedRating();
    });

    function getPaginatedRating(){
      limit+=20;
        $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: '/prod-fcp/files/review_rating.php',
        dataType: 'json',
        data : {input_supplier_id:decryptedglid, sort_type:sort_type,pagelinktype:pagelinktype, is_presnt_tstmonial:is_presnt_tstmonial, testimonialPageLink:testimonialPageLink,limit:limit},
        success: function(response){
            if(response != ''){
                    if(response.resultComments !="undefined" && response.resultComments !="" && (pagelinktype == 'testimonial' || pagelinktype == 'demotestimonial')){
                        $("#commentHTML").append(response.resultComments);
                  }
                     if(limit<$total_rating)
                    {$("#rat_more").show();
                    }
                    else{
                    $("#rat_more").hide();}

        }},
        complete: function(){
         callHelpfulEvent();
            },
        error: function(error) {
            console.log(error.responseText);}
    });
}

    $("#rat_more").on("click", getPaginatedRating);
  
        
       
function markHelpful(rat_glid,rating_id, is_helpful,source_id,ip,country){
 $.ajax({
   type:'POST',
   url:'/prod-mdc/cgi/helpful_rating.php',
   contentType:"application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
   data:{rat_glid:rat_glid, rating_id: rating_id, is_helpful: is_helpful, source_id: source_id,ip:ip,country:country},
    success: function(response){
        var res = JSON.parse(response);
        if(res &&  res.CODE ==200 &&  res.STATUS=='SUCCESS' && res.MESSAGE=='Record already exists'){
            let el = document.getElementById(`helpful-${rating_id}`);
                if(el){
                    el.innerHTML=
                    `<div style="display: flex; align-items: end; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #067D62; margin-right: 2px"><path d="M0 256C0 114.6 114.6 0 256 0C397.4 0 512 114.6 512 256C512 397.4 397.4 512 256 512C114.6 512 0 397.4 0 256zM371.8 211.8C382.7 200.9 382.7 183.1 371.8 172.2C360.9 161.3 343.1 161.3 332.2 172.2L224 280.4L179.8 236.2C168.9 225.3 151.1 225.3 140.2 236.2C129.3 247.1 129.3 264.9 140.2 275.8L204.2 339.8C215.1 350.7 232.9 350.7 243.8 339.8L371.8 211.8z"/></svg>
                    <p style="color: #067D62;">Already marked helpful.</p>
                    </div>`;}
            
        }
       else if(res &&  res.CODE ==200 &&  res.STATUS=='SUCCESS' && res.MESSAGE=='INSERT SUCCESS' ){
            let el = document.getElementById(`helpful-${rating_id}`);
                if(el){
                    el.innerHTML=
                    `<div style="display: flex; align-items: end; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #067D62; margin-right: 2px"><path d="M0 256C0 114.6 114.6 0 256 0C397.4 0 512 114.6 512 256C512 397.4 397.4 512 256 512C114.6 512 0 397.4 0 256zM371.8 211.8C382.7 200.9 382.7 183.1 371.8 172.2C360.9 161.3 343.1 161.3 332.2 172.2L224 280.4L179.8 236.2C168.9 225.3 151.1 225.3 140.2 236.2C129.3 247.1 129.3 264.9 140.2 275.8L204.2 339.8C215.1 350.7 232.9 350.7 243.8 339.8L371.8 211.8z"/></svg>
                    <p style="color: #067D62;">Thank you for your feedback.</p>
                    </div>`;}
            
        }
        else {
                console.error("Unexpected response structure", response);
            }
    },
    error: function(e){
        console.log("error");
    }
 });     
}

function checkBlloaded(){
    // Initialize BL forms
    if(typeof isBlEnqLoaded == 'undefined'){
        setTimeout(function(){checkBlloaded()},50);
    }
    else{
        if(bl_in==0)
        {
            initializeForm(inline_blenq_hash);
            bl_in=1;
        }
    }
}

            $('.enq_blform').removeClass('FM_ds4');
		   },
		   dataType: "script",
		   cache: true
		});
    }
}

          Solution

          Check the response for the potential presence of personally identifiable information (PII), ensure nothing sensitive is leaked by the application.

  2. Risk=Medium, Confidence=High (4)

    1. https://www.indiamart.com (4)

      1. CSP: Wildcard Directive (1)
        1. GET https://www.indiamart.com/sitemap.xml
          Alert tags
          • CWE-693
          • OWASP_2021_A05
          • OWASP_2017_A06
          Alert description

          Content Security Policy (CSP) is an added layer of security that helps to detect and mitigate certain types of attacks. Including (but not limited to) Cross Site Scripting (XSS), and data injection attacks. These attacks are used for everything from data theft to site defacement or distribution of malware. CSP provides a set of standard HTTP headers that allow website owners to declare approved sources of content that browsers should be allowed to load on that page — covered types are JavaScript, CSS, HTML frames, fonts, images and embeddable objects such as Java applets, ActiveX, audio and video files.
          Other info

          The following directives either allow wildcard sources (or ancestors), are not defined, or are overly broadly defined:

          img-src, connect-src, frame-src, frame-ancestors, form-action

          The directive(s): frame-ancestors, form-action are among the directives that do not fallback to default-src, missing/excluding them is the same as allowing anything.

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }

    city=(city==''||city=="null"||city==null)?'All India':city;

    var splitcity = city.toLowerCase().split(' ');

        splitcity[i] = splitcity[i].charAt(0).toUpperCase() + splitcity[i].substring(1);

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

          Ensure that your web server, application server, load balancer, etc. is properly configured to set the Content-Security-Policy header.
      2. CSP: script-src unsafe-inline (1)
        1. GET https://www.indiamart.com/sitemap.xml
          Alert tags
          • CWE-693
          • OWASP_2021_A05
          • OWASP_2017_A06
          Alert description

          Content Security Policy (CSP) is an added layer of security that helps to detect and mitigate certain types of attacks. Including (but not limited to) Cross Site Scripting (XSS), and data injection attacks. These attacks are used for everything from data theft to site defacement or distribution of malware. CSP provides a set of standard HTTP headers that allow website owners to declare approved sources of content that browsers should be allowed to load on that page — covered types are JavaScript, CSS, HTML frames, fonts, images and embeddable objects such as Java applets, ActiveX, audio and video files.

function recordOutboundLink(link, category, action, value, timeOutFlag) {
var linkHref = '';
if ( typeof(link) == 'string' && link.match(/\/\//) )
{
linkHref = link;
} else {
linkHref = link.href;
}
if(category == 'EXP')
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'optimize.activate','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else if(action == 'Fetch-0' && (category == 'Trac-Fetch-More' || category == 'Gallery-Trac-Fetch-More' ))
{   
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent-NI','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}

if ( timeOutFlag == 1 ) {
setTimeout('document.location = "' + linkHref + '"', 100);
}
}

}

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

     <script>
        function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

        var cookie = readCookie("ImeshVisitor");
        if ( cookie != ""){
        var namep=getparamVal(decodeURIComponent(cookie), 'fn');
        var forname = '<span class="rmv Hd_dib cpo ico-usr Hd_pr">Hi <span class="Hd_dib Hd_pr">'+namep+'</span></span>';
        document.getElementById("lshead").innerHTML = forname;
        }
        else{
            var sgnhtm = '<a class="rmv Hd_dib cpo ico-usr" href="https://my.indiamart.com"><span class="Hd_pr">Sign In</span></a>';
            document.getElementById("lshead").innerHTML = sgnhtm;
        }

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

        1. GET https://www.indiamart.com/sitemap.xml
          Alert tags
          • CWE-693
          • OWASP_2021_A05
          • OWASP_2017_A06
          Alert description

          Content Security Policy (CSP) is an added layer of security that helps to detect and mitigate certain types of attacks. Including (but not limited to) Cross Site Scripting (XSS), and data injection attacks. These attacks are used for everything from data theft to site defacement or distribution of malware. CSP provides a set of standard HTTP headers that allow website owners to declare approved sources of content that browsers should be allowed to load on that page — covered types are JavaScript, CSS, HTML frames, fonts, images and embeddable objects such as Java applets, ActiveX, audio and video files.

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');

        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        return "";

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);

      4. Content Security Policy (CSP) Header Not Set (1)

          Alert tags

          Alert description

          Content Security Policy (CSP) is an added layer of security that helps to detect and mitigate certain types of attacks, including Cross Site Scripting (XSS) and data injection attacks. These attacks are used for everything from data theft to site defacement or distribution of malware. CSP provides a set of standard HTTP headers that allow website owners to declare approved sources of content that browsers should be allowed to load on that page — covered types are JavaScript, CSS, HTML frames, fonts, images and embeddable objects such as Java applets, ActiveX, audio and video files.

  3. Risk=Medium, Confidence=Low (1)

    1. https://www.indiamart.com (1)

      1. Absence of Anti-CSRF Tokens (1)
        1. GET https://www.indiamart.com/sitemap.xml
          Alert tags
          • OWASP_2021_A01
          • WSTG-v42-SESS-05
          • OWASP_2017_A05
          • CWE-352
          Alert description

          No Anti-CSRF tokens were found in a HTML submission form.

          A cross-site request forgery is an attack that involves forcing a victim to send an HTTP request to a target destination without their knowledge or intent in order to perform an action as the victim. The underlying cause is application functionality using predictable URL/form actions in a repeatable way. The nature of the attack is that CSRF exploits the trust that a web site has for a user. By contrast, cross-site scripting (XSS) exploits the trust that a user has for a web site. Like XSS, CSRF attacks are not necessarily cross-site, but they can be. Cross-site request forgery is also known as CSRF, XSRF, one-click attack, session riding, confused deputy, and sea surf.

          CSRF attacks are effective in a number of situations, including:

          * The victim has an active session on the target site.

          * The victim is authenticated via HTTP auth on the target site.

          * The victim is on the same local network as the target site.

          CSRF has primarily been used to perform an action against a target site using the victim's privileges, but recent techniques have been discovered to disclose information by gaining access to the response. The risk of information disclosure is dramatically increased when the target site is vulnerable to XSS, because XSS can be used as a platform for CSRF, allowing the attack to operate within the bounds of the same-origin policy.
          Other info

          No known Anti-CSRF token [anticsrf, CSRFToken, __RequestVerificationToken, csrfmiddlewaretoken, authenticity_token, OWASP_CSRFTOKEN, anoncsrf, csrf_token, _csrf, _csrfSecret, __csrf_magic, CSRF, _token, _csrf_token] was found in the following HTML form: [Form 1: "btnSearch" "search_string" ].

{

}

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

     <script>
        function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

          Solution

          Phase: Architecture and Design

          Use a vetted library or framework that does not allow this weakness to occur or provides constructs that make this weakness easier to avoid.

          For example, use anti-CSRF packages such as the OWASP CSRFGuard.

          Phase: Implementation

          Ensure that your application is free of cross-site scripting issues, because most CSRF defenses can be bypassed using attacker-controlled script.

          Phase: Architecture and Design

          Generate a unique nonce for each form, place the nonce into the form, and verify the nonce upon receipt of the form. Be sure that the nonce is not predictable (CWE-330).

          Note that this can be bypassed using XSS.

          Identify especially dangerous operations. When the user performs a dangerous operation, send a separate confirmation request to ensure that the user intended to perform that operation.

          Note that this can be bypassed using XSS.

          Use the ESAPI Session Management control.

          This control includes a component for CSRF.

          Do not use the GET method for any request that triggers a state change.

          Phase: Implementation

          Check the HTTP Referer header to see if the request originated from an expected page. This could break legitimate functionality, because users or proxies may have disabled sending the Referer for privacy reasons.

     <script>
        function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
        var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

        var cookie = readCookie("ImeshVisitor");
        if ( cookie != ""){

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

          A cookie has been set without the HttpOnly flag, which means that the cookie can be accessed by JavaScript. function recordOutboundLink(link, category, action, value, timeOutFlag) {
var linkHref = '';
if ( typeof(link) == 'string' && link.match(/\/\//) )
{
linkHref = link;
} else {
linkHref = link.href;
}
if(category == 'EXP')
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'optimize.activate','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else if(action == 'Fetch-0' && (category == 'Trac-Fetch-More' || category == 'Gallery-Trac-Fetch-More' ))
{   
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent-NI','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}

if ( timeOutFlag == 1 ) {
setTimeout('document.location = "' + linkHref + '"', 100);
}
}

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');

        var c = ca[i];

        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }

        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        return "";
            }

    city=(city==''||city=="null"||city==null)?'All India':city;
    city=city.replace('-', ' ');
    var splitcity = city.toLowerCase().split(' ');

        splitcity[i] = splitcity[i].charAt(0).toUpperCase() + splitcity[i].substring(1);

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

          Solution

          Whenever a cookie contains sensitive information or is a session token, then it should always be passed using an encrypted channel. Ensure that the secure flag is set for cookies containing such sensitive information.

function recordOutboundLink(link, category, action, value, timeOutFlag) {
var linkHref = '';
if ( typeof(link) == 'string' && link.match(/\/\//) )
{
linkHref = link;
} else {
linkHref = link.href;
}
if(category == 'EXP')
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'optimize.activate','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else if(action == 'Fetch-0' && (category == 'Trac-Fetch-More' || category == 'Gallery-Trac-Fetch-More' ))
{   
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent-NI','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}

if ( timeOutFlag == 1 ) {
setTimeout('document.location = "' + linkHref + '"', 100);
}
}

}

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

     <script>
        function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        function getparamVal(cookieStr, key) {
        if (cookieStr > "") {

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'optimize.activate','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else if(action == 'Fetch-0' && (category == 'Trac-Fetch-More' || category == 'Gallery-Trac-Fetch-More' ))
{   
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent-NI','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}

if ( timeOutFlag == 1 ) {
setTimeout('document.location = "' + linkHref + '"', 100);
}
}

}

    'eventAction': array[2],

    'eventValue': array[4] 
        });
        
  }
  }

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        if (cookieStr > "") {
        var val = "|" + cookieStr + "|";
        var pattern = new RegExp(".*?\\|" + key + "=([^|]*).*|.*");
        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }
        }

function hdr_getusercity(city){
    var city =city||"All India";
    city=(city==''||city=="null"||city==null)?'All India':city;
    city=city.replace('-', ' ');
    var splitcity = city.toLowerCase().split(' ');
    for (var i = 0; i < splitcity.length; i++) {
        splitcity[i] = splitcity[i].charAt(0).toUpperCase() + splitcity[i].substring(1);  
    }
    city = splitcity.join(' ');
    var hddrpdn2 = '<button id="hd_searchPlace" class="hd_cFl cpo"><span id="hd_usercity" class="Hd_db">'+city+'</span></button><div id="city_hold" class="hd_cSrb Hd_dbn"><label for="hd_city_sugg"></label><input type="text" id="hd_city_sugg" placeholder ="Enter City" value ="Enter City" class="srin ui-autocomplete-input" autocomplete="off" role="textbox" aria-autocomplete="list" aria-haspopup="true" onkeyup="AlInd_Op()"><div class="hd_alop Hd_dbn cpo" id="all_India" >All India</div></div>';

        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};
</script><div id="rvw_img_pop" class="FM_ds4">

<h2 class="FM_f26 FM_c1"><p id="aboutus" class="namePlace-1 FM_pa FM_ps_r FM_ps_l"></p><a href="profile.html" class="FM_pr FM_pb5">About Us<span class="FM_bgH prd_hd FM_ps_b FM_ps_l FM_ps_r FM_mAuto FM_pa"></span></a></h2>
</div><div class="FM_f16 Fm_lh3 FM_m9 FM_txc pl30 pr30"><span class="FM_Db FM_H_abt-1 FM_ovh FM_c7" id="homePageDesc" >Atlas&nbsp;Copco&nbsp;(India) Ltd, established in 1960, we provide our customers with the solutions they need to enhance productivity and achieve their manufacturing goals. We are a part of the&nbsp;Atlas&nbsp;Copco&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;a world-leading provider of sustainable productivity solutions&nbsp;with extensive local presence, specializing in Industrial Power Tools, Material Removal Tools, Hydraulic torque tools and Assembly solutions for a wide&nbsp;range of industry segments including general engineering, aerospace, automotive, manufacturing and process industries, oil and gas, construction, food and beverage, Chemical, among others.
&nbsp;
The other business areas of&nbsp;Atlas&nbsp;Copco&nbsp;group also provide Compressed Air and Gas Solutions, Construction Equipment and Portable Energy products throughout the globe. Our nationwide service personnel are always close at hand to provide repairs, service and spare parts locally with state-of-the-art manufacturing facilities today at Pune. function callHelpfulEvent(){
            document.querySelectorAll('.FM_hlp_rvw').forEach(item => {
                
                    item.addEventListener('click', event => {
                        
                        var im_iss = getCartCookie("im_iss");
                        if(im_iss == ""){
                           signIn('','','','B');
                            return;
                        }
                         var is_imesh = readCookie("ImeshVisitor");
                         var rat_glid='';
                         if(is_imesh != ""){
                           rat_glid=getparamVal(is_imesh, "glid");
                         }
                        var ip_cookie = getCartCookie("iploc");
                        var ip=''; var country='';
                        if(ip_cookie!= ""){
                            ip=getparamVal(ip_cookie, "gip");
                            country=getparamVal(ip_cookie, "gcnnm");
                        }
                        
                        markHelpful(rat_glid,item.id,1,source_id,ip,country); //calling markhelpful function for testimonial
                    });
                });
            }
            //for calling the helful functionality on first page load
            $(document).ready(function(){
    callHelpfulEvent();
});
function getRatingAjax(){
        $.ajax({
            type: "POST",
            url: '/prod-fcp/files/review_rating.php',
            dataType: 'json',
            data : {input_supplier_id:decryptedglid, sort_type:sort_type,pagelinktype:pagelinktype, is_presnt_tstmonial:is_presnt_tstmonial, testimonialPageLink:testimonialPageLink,limit:limit},
            success: function(response)
            {
                if(response != ''){
                    if(response.resultTop !="undefined" && response.resultTop !=""){
                        $("#review_data").html(response.resultTop);
                        if(response.resultComments !="undefined" && response.resultComments !="" && (pagelinktype == 'testimonial' || pagelinktype == 'demotestimonial'))
                            $("#commentHTML").html(response.resultComments);
                        
                }
                }
            },
            beforeSend: function(){
                $('.loader').show();
            },
            complete: function(){
                $('.loader').hide();
                callHelpfulEvent();
            },
            error: function(error) {
                console.log(error.responseText);
            }
        });
    }

    $('.FM_sortng').change(function(){
       limit = 20;
        sort_type = $('#sortValue').val();
        if(limit<$total_rating)
            {$("#rat_more").show();}
        else{
            $("#rat_more").hide();}
        if(limit==20)
        getRatingAjax();
        else
        getPaginatedRating();
    });

    function getPaginatedRating(){
      limit+=20;
        $.ajax({
        type: "POST",
        url: '/prod-fcp/files/review_rating.php',
        dataType: 'json',
        data : {input_supplier_id:decryptedglid, sort_type:sort_type,pagelinktype:pagelinktype, is_presnt_tstmonial:is_presnt_tstmonial, testimonialPageLink:testimonialPageLink,limit:limit},
        success: function(response){
            if(response != ''){
                    if(response.resultComments !="undefined" && response.resultComments !="" && (pagelinktype == 'testimonial' || pagelinktype == 'demotestimonial')){
                        $("#commentHTML").append(response.resultComments);
                  }
                     if(limit<$total_rating)
                    {$("#rat_more").show();
                    }
                    else{
                    $("#rat_more").hide();}

        }},
        complete: function(){
         callHelpfulEvent();
            },
        error: function(error) {
            console.log(error.responseText);}
    });
}

    $("#rat_more").on("click", getPaginatedRating);

function markHelpful(rat_glid,rating_id, is_helpful,source_id,ip,country){
 $.ajax({
   type:'POST',
   url:'/prod-mdc/cgi/helpful_rating.php',
   contentType:"application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
   data:{rat_glid:rat_glid, rating_id: rating_id, is_helpful: is_helpful, source_id: source_id,ip:ip,country:country},
    success: function(response){
        var res = JSON.parse(response);
        if(res &&  res.CODE ==200 &&  res.STATUS=='SUCCESS' && res.MESSAGE=='Record already exists'){
            let el = document.getElementById(`helpful-${rating_id}`);
                if(el){
                    el.innerHTML=
                    `<div style="display: flex; align-items: end; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #067D62; margin-right: 2px"><path d="M0 256C0 114.6 114.6 0 256 0C397.4 0 512 114.6 512 256C512 397.4 397.4 512 256 512C114.6 512 0 397.4 0 256zM371.8 211.8C382.7 200.9 382.7 183.1 371.8 172.2C360.9 161.3 343.1 161.3 332.2 172.2L224 280.4L179.8 236.2C168.9 225.3 151.1 225.3 140.2 236.2C129.3 247.1 129.3 264.9 140.2 275.8L204.2 339.8C215.1 350.7 232.9 350.7 243.8 339.8L371.8 211.8z"/></svg>
                    <p style="color: #067D62;">Already marked helpful.</p>
                    </div>`;}
            
        }
       else if(res &&  res.CODE ==200 &&  res.STATUS=='SUCCESS' && res.MESSAGE=='INSERT SUCCESS' ){
            let el = document.getElementById(`helpful-${rating_id}`);
                if(el){
                    el.innerHTML=
                    `<div style="display: flex; align-items: end; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #067D62; margin-right: 2px"><path d="M0 256C0 114.6 114.6 0 256 0C397.4 0 512 114.6 512 256C512 397.4 397.4 512 256 512C114.6 512 0 397.4 0 256zM371.8 211.8C382.7 200.9 382.7 183.1 371.8 172.2C360.9 161.3 343.1 161.3 332.2 172.2L224 280.4L179.8 236.2C168.9 225.3 151.1 225.3 140.2 236.2C129.3 247.1 129.3 264.9 140.2 275.8L204.2 339.8C215.1 350.7 232.9 350.7 243.8 339.8L371.8 211.8z"/></svg>
                    <p style="color: #067D62;">Thank you for your feedback.</p>
                    </div>`;}
            
        }
        else {
                console.error("Unexpected response structure", response);
            }
    },
    error: function(e){
        console.log("error");
    }
 });     
}

function checkBlloaded(){
    // Initialize BL forms
    if(typeof isBlEnqLoaded == 'undefined'){
        setTimeout(function(){checkBlloaded()},50);
    }
    else{
        if(bl_in==0)
        {
            initializeForm(inline_blenq_hash);
            bl_in=1;
        }
    }
}

function load_enqjs() {
    if(typeof OpenForm == "undefined" && is_loaded_blenqpost_js == 0){
    is_loaded_blenqpost_js=1;
     $.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "https://apps.imimg.com/js/enqBl_desktop.min.js?v=313",
		   success: function(){
		   setTimeout(function(){ try {checkBlloaded();} catch (e) {}}, 50);
            $('.enq_blform').removeClass('FM_ds4');
		   },
		   dataType: "script",
		   cache: true
		});
    }
}

function pers_widget(glid)
{

if(pwidget == 0){
if(typeof(perWidget)!="undefined" && typeof (fetchPersProds) == "function" && typeof sugg != 'undefined' && typeof sugg.recent == 'function'){
    fetchPersProds({ modid: "FCP", count: 10, 'callRelatedAPI': true })
            .then(result => {
                persFeatArr = result;  
                attachFeaturedHTML(persFeatArr);             
            })
            .catch(error => {
                console.log('Error: ', error);
            });
pwidget=1;

}
else
{
setTimeout(function(){pers_widget(glid)},50);
}
}
}

    $('#return-to-top').fadeOut();

 }

});

    function readCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + "=";
        try {
            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {
            var decodedCookie = unescape(document.cookie);
        }
        var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
        for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
        c = c.substring(1);
         }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            }
        return "";
        }

        return val.replace(pattern, '$1');
        } else {
        return "";
            }

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

function recordOutboundLink(link, category, action, value, timeOutFlag) {
var linkHref = '';
if ( typeof(link) == 'string' && link.match(/\/\//) )
{
linkHref = link;
} else {
linkHref = link.href;
}
if(category == 'EXP')
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'optimize.activate','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else if(action == 'Fetch-0' && (category == 'Trac-Fetch-More' || category == 'Gallery-Trac-Fetch-More' ))
{   
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent-NI','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}

if ( timeOutFlag == 1 ) {
setTimeout('document.location = "' + linkHref + '"', 100);
}
}

}

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

          Solution

          Remove all comments that return information that may help an attacker and fix any underlying problems they refer to.
      2. Loosely Scoped Cookie (1)
        1. GET https://www.indiamart.com/pd/
          Alert tags
          • OWASP_2021_A08
          • CWE-565
          • OWASP_2017_A06
          • WSTG-v42-SESS-02
          Alert description

          Cookies can be scoped by domain or path. This check is only concerned with domain scope.The domain scope applied to a cookie determines which domains can access it. For example, a cookie can be scoped strictly to a subdomain e.g. www.nottrusted.com, or loosely scoped to a parent domain e.g. nottrusted.com. In the latter case, any subdomain of nottrusted.com can access the cookie. Loosely scoped cookies are common in mega-applications like google.com and live.com. Cookies set from a subdomain like app.foo.bar are transmitted only to that domain by the browser. However, cookies scoped to a parent-level domain may be transmitted to the parent, or any subdomain of the parent.

function recordOutboundLink(link, category, action, value, timeOutFlag) {
var linkHref = '';
if ( typeof(link) == 'string' && link.match(/\/\//) )
{
linkHref = link;
} else {
linkHref = link.href;
}
if(category == 'EXP')
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'optimize.activate','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else if(action == 'Fetch-0' && (category == 'Trac-Fetch-More' || category == 'Gallery-Trac-Fetch-More' ))
{   
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent-NI','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}
else
{
    imgtm.push({ 'event' : 'IMEvent','eventCategory' : category,'eventAction' : action,'eventLabel' : linkHref,'eventValue': value});
}

setTimeout('document.location = "' + linkHref + '"', 100);
}
}

    function readCookie(cname) {

            var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
        } catch(err) {

function setHdCountry()
{
    var hdIploc='',hdCcode='';
    var hdSrch="iploc=";
    if (document.cookie.length > 0){
        var offset = document.cookie.indexOf(hdSrch);
        if (offset != -1){
            offset += hdSrch.length;
            end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
            if (end == -1)
                end = document.cookie.length;
            hdIploc=unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
        }
    }
    if(hdIploc != '' && hdIploc.indexOf('gcniso=') != -1){
   
        var hdcon = hdIploc.split('gcniso=');
        if(typeof(hdcon[1])!="undefined")
            var hdcarr = hdcon[1].split('|');
        hdCcode= hdcarr[0];
    }
    if(hdCcode == '')
    {
        var hdDate = new Date();
        var hdgmt = -hdDate.getTimezoneOffset() / 60;
        if (hdgmt != 5.5)
            hdCcode = 'OTHER';
        else
            hdCcode = 'IN';
    }
    if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode == 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^\+91/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('+91-','0');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
    else if(typeof(hdCcode)!="undefined" && hdCcode != '' && hdCcode != 'IN')
    {
        var hdInpt = document.getElementsByClassName('duet');
        for (var i = 0, len = hdInpt.length; i < len; i++) {
            var hdMid = hdInpt[i];
            var hdContent = hdMid.innerHTML;
            if(hdContent.match(/^0/)){
                hdContent = hdContent.replace('0','+91-');
                hdMid.innerHTML=hdContent;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
    window.addEventListener("load", function(){setHdCountry();}, false);
else if (window.attachEvent)
    window.attachEvent("onload", function(){setHdCountry();});
else
    window.onload = function(){setHdCountry();};

function loadScrpt(url) {
    if (typeof(url) !== 'undefined' && url !== '') {
        var script = document.createElement("script")
        script.type = "text/javascript";
        if (script.readyState) { //IE
            script.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (script.readyState == "loaded" ||
                    script.readyState == "complete") {
                    script.onreadystatechange = null;
                }
            };
        }
        script.src = url;
        document.body.appendChild(script);
    }
}

        {
            PersonalizedWidget({widgetID:'W5',modID:'DIR_NotFound',glusrID:glid});
        }
    }
    else
    {
        setTimeout(function(){pers_widget(glid)},50);
    }
}

      3. Re-examine Cache-control Directives (1)
        1. GET https://www.indiamart.com/robots.txt
          Alert tags
          • WSTG-v42-ATHN-06
          • CWE-525
          Alert description

          The cache-control header has not been set properly or is missing, allowing the browser and proxies to cache content. For static assets like css, js, or image files this might be intended, however, the resources should be reviewed to ensure that no sensitive content will be cached.

          Parameter 
          cache-control
          Solution

          For secure content, ensure the cache-control HTTP header is set with "no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate". If an asset should be cached consider setting the directives "public, max-age, immutable".

Appendix

Alert types

This section contains additional information on the types of alerts in the report.

  1. PII Disclosure

    Source raised by a passive scanner (PII Disclosure)
    CWE ID 359
    WASC ID 13

  2. Absence of Anti-CSRF Tokens

    Source raised by a passive scanner (Absence of Anti-CSRF Tokens)
    CWE ID 352
    WASC ID 9
    Reference
    1. https://cheatsheetseries.owasp.org/cheatsheets/Cross-Site_Request_Forgery_Prevention_Cheat_Sheet.html
    2. https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/352.html

  3. CSP: Wildcard Directive

    Source raised by a passive scanner (CSP)
    CWE ID 693
    WASC ID 15
    Reference
    1. https://www.w3.org/TR/CSP/
    2. https://caniuse.com/#search=content+security+policy
    3. https://content-security-policy.com/
    4. https://github.com/HtmlUnit/htmlunit-csp
    5. https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/security/csp#policy_applies_to_a_wide_variety_of_resources

  4. CSP: script-src unsafe-inline

    Source raised by a passive scanner (CSP)
    CWE ID 693
    WASC ID 15
    Reference
    1. https://www.w3.org/TR/CSP/
    2. https://caniuse.com/#search=content+security+policy
    3. https://content-security-policy.com/
    4. https://github.com/HtmlUnit/htmlunit-csp
    5. https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/security/csp#policy_applies_to_a_wide_variety_of_resources

  5. CSP: style-src unsafe-inline

    Source raised by a passive scanner (CSP)
    CWE ID 693
    WASC ID 15
    Reference
    1. https://www.w3.org/TR/CSP/
    2. https://caniuse.com/#search=content+security+policy
    3. https://content-security-policy.com/
    4. https://github.com/HtmlUnit/htmlunit-csp
    5. https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/security/csp#policy_applies_to_a_wide_variety_of_resources

  6. Content Security Policy (CSP) Header Not Set

    Source raised by a passive scanner (Content Security Policy (CSP) Header Not Set)
    CWE ID 693
    WASC ID 15
    Reference
    1. https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Security/CSP/Introducing_Content_Security_Policy
